Package logic.player.ai

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AIGame.Position
    Represents the position of a piece on the board or in a player's hand.

    Represents a move that can be performed in the game.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AIGame
    An extension of the Game class with details specific to the AI player.
    Represents a game of Animal Chess.
    AIPlayer
    Represents an AI player.
    Represents a player in the game.
    AIPlayer.BoardMove
    Represents a move from one board position to another.
    AIPlayer.PlaceMove
    Represents a move from a player's hand to the board.
